Q: Should we include PSI pids in the PID lookup table?
Not sure what is the best.  Will use separate lookup first!


Q: How to pass info between input thread and PSI thread.
The following info are needed for each PSI TP:
  - tp_addr
  - in_session 
Difficult to fit them into the 32-bit pulse code.
Instead, we create a tp_info for each PSI TP.  The address of the tp_info
will be used in the pulse code.
